Hi!

I just wrote my first Open Type feature, but it doesn't work! I was trying to acheive a simple glyph substitution:

feature liga {  
 sub A E by AE;  
} liga;

As I hit the »Compile« Button, the following Message appeared:

[FATAL] aborting because of errors:  
syntax error at "feature"  
[/Users/jurgen/Library/Application Support/FontLab/Studio 5/Features/fontlab.fea 6]

Why? What can I do?

Thanks in advance,  
Juergen
